This complete codebase provides:

1. Clean HTML/CSS/JS frontend with Bootstrap styling
2. Node.js/Express backend with MongoDB integration
3. INR currency support throughout the application
4. All requested features including alerts, search, filtering, and export
5. Mobile-responsive design for phone browser access
6. Ready-to-deploy structure with proper configuration files

To use this code:

1. Export your Lovable project to GitHub
2. Replace the contents with these files
3. Set up MongoDB Atlas and add your connection string to .env
4. Run npm install and npm run dev
5. Open client/index.html in your browser
6. The system is production-ready and includes all the features you requested for your father's pharmacy inventory management.